# Sample Style Guide Used

- Boolean variables are to be either yes or no.  NOT true/false
- Spaces in filenames should be represented by an underscore _
- Spaces in varialbes should be represented by an underscore _
- Spaces in role names should be represented by an underscore -
- 2 spaces for indentation
- whitespacing - use of comments (which start with ‘# ’), is encouraged (Thats a # followed by a space).

